  "text": "This meta-analysis provides evidence for the beneficial effect of face-to-face-based psychosocial interventions on the quality of life of CRC patients. Of course, it is still premature to generalize these findings, as the identified effect size was small. Given that quality of life changes with time and emphasizes the importance of personal growth [CITATION_1] , it may take time to fully detect ",
